Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,ONTO PAPNICA KINGDOM
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you fought well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially Dai.\NThis victory was thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly have grown into one\Nworthy of the title "Hero."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,From this day on,\Nyou may call yourself, "Dai, the Hero."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dream came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, it's too soon for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have won alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, Maam, Gomechan, and everyone in the\Ncastle worked together for this victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm a Hero, then everyone is a Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So, until I get a little stronger\Nand can fight without burdening anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't call me a Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:03:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.\NI look forward to your further growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Brass, you truly have raised\Na good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes. He's... He's my pride and joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, Grampa.\NThat's called over-doting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You imbecile! Nobody asked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,These gifts are the least I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wear them and go show the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone wants to see\Nthe heroes who saved this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear he's still a small boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to catch a glimpse\Nof the mighty Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Those youths are the ones who saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Our heroes! Hurrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:04:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, real Heroes look so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fought now, you probably won't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems you're the real deal after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good luck to you, boy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels pretty good to work hard\Nand have people thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, you're actually a little cool today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Thank you for your cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai, listen to them cheer for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While you may not wish it yet,\NI'm sure the people will speak of you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as "Dai, the Tiny Hero."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It came from the Heart Chamber!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:05:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Heart Chamber?\NThat's where Magic Rituals are held.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Begirama,\Nthe most powerful Heat-type spell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Along with that new body of yours,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}accept it as your reward for slaying Avan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I have mastered both\NHeat and Explosion-type spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadlar...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your Heyedras\Nand send an order to all our forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Summon the remaining Legion Commanders\Nhere at Sovereign Rock Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai, until the day the Dark King\Nis defeated and peace is restored,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we shall live quietly\Nhere on Dermline Island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:06:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, Dai, don't worry about us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fight on with all your might.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo! This is exhilarating!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe King Romos just casually\Nlent us a ship. He's so magnanimous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And man, is this ship fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't say goodbye to Brass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was too hard for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll just have to\Ncheer him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the long face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you care about your old man,\Nbut you don't need to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All we got to do is wipe out\Nthe Dark King and your problem's solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. We just have to do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. It'll be fine.\NYou've got strong allies at your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,With me here, you've got nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,With that last battle,\NI feel my caliber as a man,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,or as a Mage,\Nreally leveled up like crazy--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Leveled up like crazy," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry if you were startled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This ship continuously pours out\NHoly Water as it sails.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your average monster can't even get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. That sounds lavish.\NNothing like the tub we sailed over in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. You could never make it\Nto the Continent of Holkia with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Continent of Holkia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show you on a map!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're heading east, past Dermline Island,\Nto the Continent of Holkia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Papnica is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Dermline Island is so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But why head to Papnica?\NThere are other large countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's to see\Nhis beloved princess, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not the only reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Beloved princess"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's friends with the princess of Papnica.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he wants to rescue her\Nfrom the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite the ladies' man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Look at him blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. But the princess of Papnica, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Army has sent legions\Nto each continent for an invasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but I hear the battle in Papnica\Nhas been the most intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I've heard, 15 years ago, Holkia\Nwas the Dark Lord Hadlar's main base.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadlar's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, that's why the most\Nterrifying Legion of the Dark Army
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,has been sent to take\Nthe Continent of Holkia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They say, its a legion of immortals\Ncalled "the Undead."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A legion of immortals...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leona...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be there soon! Just hold on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.76,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,NORTHERN COUNTRY OF ORZAM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.70,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,BLIZZBLAZE LEGION LEGION COMMANDER\NBLIZZBLAZE GENERAL FLAZZARD
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Frail! They're all so frail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do humans have such fragile bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If these are their best warriors,\Nthen this country is all but mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Flazzard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Flazzard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We've just received a message\Nfrom a Heyedra!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All Legion Commanders are to gather\Nat Sovereign Rock Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems a new young Hero\Nhas risen and defeated Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So it's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'm going to Sovereign Rock Castle.\NYou finish off this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn the villages\Nand put the surviving humans in ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave no trace of the humans,\Nbe it house, field or even livestock!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:10:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:10.52,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Avan Strash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:15.52,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}HELL'S CLAW{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Blizzblaze General Flazzard has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Flazzard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Oh, Zaboera, the geezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,As fast as ever, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You live up to your name of\N"Blitz Captain of the Dark Army."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Crocodine was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How pathetic. To lose to a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that boy, Dai,\Nis not to be underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I offered a sure-fire scheme\Nand he still lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's placed in Resurrection Fluid,\Nbut his chances are 50% at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:12:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If whoever caused this wound really is\Njust a kid, then he's a damn monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No one, no matter how strong, can damage\NCrocodine's steel body this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He must possess more than\Njust physical power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not bad, Blizzblaze General Flazzard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not just some hot-blooded brawler, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having both flaming brutality\Nand ice-cold cunningness...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I concur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This new Hero possesses great potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:31.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,DRAGON LEGION LEGION COMMANDER\NDRAGON MASTER GENERAL BARAN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My sympathies, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Heading off to take Ringaia and then\Nbeing summoned right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sympathies are unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already crushed Ringaia Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?!\N-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadlar awaits\Nin the Left Shoulder Chamber. Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He wiped out the Fortress Kingdom\Nof Ringaia in such a short time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's as powerful\Nas a wrathful god just as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for coming so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm. I see Master Hadlar\Nhas gained more power again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's as though power oozes from him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It appears his seat as Dark Commander\Nremains secure for now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That leaves Mystvearn and Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell is late\Nfor an emergency summons?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Flazzard, didn't you notice\NMystvearn is already seated?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,SHADOW LEGION LEGION COMMANDER\NMYSTVEARN, THE SHADOW VIZIER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You?! When the hell...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Always the unsociable one, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That leaves Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it appears\NI must apologize to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I intended to gather our forces\Nand crush the new Hero, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:14:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But Dark King Vearn\Nhas made a direct order.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave the task\Nof slaying Dai to Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really the famous\Nscenic port city of Papnica?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, this place is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we're off the ship,\Nget away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?\NIf he does that, our ride back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time\Nto be worried about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please be okay, Leona!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible. I doubt any survivors...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,S-S-S-Skeletons!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be the immortal legion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They invaded this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Dai! We're clearly outnumbered!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fine then.\NIt looks like we have to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Avan Style\NSword Technique Earth Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he's a Disciple of Avan, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know there were other users of\Nthe Avan Style Sword Technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's a Disciple of Avan,\NI'm sure he'll join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?\NHe's got the face of a villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a student of Avan, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that\NI learned to fight from Avan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm to be called a student of Avan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,then I would be the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! You're his first student?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a freaky sword.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never seen a sword\Nso ominous and eerie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's got a strange, malicious feel to him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he really on our side?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us what happened to this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It fell to the Undead Legion\Nof the Dark Army two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Undead Legion?!\NYou mean those skeletons?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Leona?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what happened\Nto the princess of this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea. I was wondering that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an outrage! Hyunckel?!\NThat little pipsqueak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I never liked the fact that\Neven though he's just a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,he was accepted as a Legion Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Flazzard.\NYou're heating the place up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to calm down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand your rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But this was\Nour Dark King Vearn's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the whole thing\Nwas Hyunckel's idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because the Dark King took a liking\Nto him, he gets all uppity! That brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mystvearn...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The shadow being who can remain silent\Nfor decades at a time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's laughing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark King's words\Ntake precedence above all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice but to obey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Hyunckel\Nis the perfect choice for killing Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai cannot defeat Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We were lucky to meet you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Join us and fight with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's off here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Only a student of Master Avan\Ncould use Earth Slash, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're really a student of Avan,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,then you should have\Nan Insignia of Avan like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,An Insignia of Avan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He really has one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We need all the help we can get!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, fight with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just laughing\Nat what fools you all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you! He's a villain after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But his Insignia of Avan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not all students of Avan\Nrespect their teacher and love justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them love violence\Nand have embraced the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,After seeing just how weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,justice really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the Six Legion Commanders\Nof the Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:44.16,On Top,,0,0,0,,UNDEAD LEGION LEGION COMMANDER\NHYUNCKEL, THE DARK SWORDSMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, the Undead Legion Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But... How could a student of Master Avan\Nbe a Legion Commander of the Dark Army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,These are resurrected corpse warriors\Nwho have surpassed death!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They will not stop their advance\Nunless pulverized!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait Hyunckel! Haven't you heard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Avan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Avan was killed! By the Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Hadlar killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet you still fight\Nfor the Dark Army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was quite a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He was killed by an enemy\Nhe once defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he gets for taking on students\Nwhile neglecting his own training.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping to kill him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Vearn, the Dark King,\Nto let me wipe out his students,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but to run into weaklings like you\Nis such a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth Slash...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't disrespect Master Avan any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive anyone\Nwho talks like that! Take it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if I say I won't?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He blocked Earth Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Reexamine your skills\Nbefore your run your mouth, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Avan Style Sword Technique {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Wave Slash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Hyunckel's sword beats Dai's\Nin both strength and skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know all about\Nthe Avan Style Sword Technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dodging someone of your skill is easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That stance...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Avan Strash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:25.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:32.91,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:36.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:46.63,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:52.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:57.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:01.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:08.11,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
